dialog.body: Hello, thank you for contacting Old Stone Auto Insurance. My name is Henry Adams. May I please have your name?
Hi Henry, my name is Kathleen Baker.
Hello, Kathleen. Thank you for providing your name. Can you please confirm your policy number with us for security purposes?
Certainly, my policy number is three two one four five.
Thank you, Kathleen. Could you also provide me with your date of birth to verify your identity and access your account details?
Yes, my date of birth is zero six two five one nine eight eight.
Great, thank you for confirming that, Kathleen. Is there anything specific I can assist you with today regarding your policy or any recent incidents?
I'd like to inquire about adding a new vehicle to my policy.
Of course, Kathleen. I can assist you with that request. Let me gather some information from you to proceed.
Thank you for your time today, Kathleen. If you have any further questions or need assistance in the future, feel free to reach out to us. Have a great day!
